5acb9eeea755c7d279","tid":1520,"uid":16477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T03:04:16.000Z","msg":"大家唔好怪佢啦 佢係我得八歲智商既表弟黎<br />\n本來細個精精靈靈幾醒目下架<br />\n點知有日比佢撞破左我un緊佢老母<br />\n我又係衰既 好似莫雷拉咁起勢騎住佢老母屌<br />\n一個唔小心騎得太快 射d精由佢老母個西度噴上個口再打中樓主塊面<br />\n可能因為撞擊力太大搞到佢傻撚左"},{"pid":"62f8027eff4920616decb55910fa600595ed4b42","tid":1520,"uid":271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T03:05:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"086b4eaf75ca028b68a418fbd6c594e203f4dfd5","tid":1520,"uid":8959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T03:06:05.000Z","msg":"第一次睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">喺lihkg</span>"},{"pid":"41cc6da1de4427ed03dd247bf53e2ffde4862665","tid":1520,"uid":7772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T03:42:24.000Z","msg":"係呢邊都仲睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa618eca3ab575a4edecb54022ff5bb8f03316f2","tid":1520,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T03:49:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c3f59e3fbd489061e418565b4979b9045513828","tid":1520,"uid":11354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:08:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a236295bf25e638645c3eaa71a689a40807f7c5b","tid":1520,"uid":42133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:10:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>梁朝偉都用LIHKG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hk